<h1 class="text-center">Resourcer the project planner.</h1>

<p class="lead text-center">
  Resourcer is a simple project planning tool. In Resourcer you can create projects and issues share them with coworkers or friends. Markdown is used for a simple issue formating. It is also possible to assign issues, set due dates and create hierarchical relationships between issues.
</p>

<div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center mt-5">
<%= button_to "/auth/github", class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" do %>
  <%= inline_svg_tag "@fortawesome/fontawesome-free/svgs/brands/github.svg", class: "svg-icon svg-icon--xl mr-2" %>
  Continue with Github
<% end %>


<%= button_to "/auth/google_oauth2", class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg mt-3 mb-5" do %>
  <%= inline_svg_tag "@fortawesome/fontawesome-free/svgs/brands/google.svg", class: "svg-icon svg-icon--xl mr-2" %>
  Continue with Google
<% end %>
</div>

<% if Rails.env.development? %>
  <%= button_to "Developer", "/auth/developer" %>
<% end %>
